Pleasure house021604apfrm9vccfdzlopshglrdy0rulze7jp1784902015-03-22T03:07:44ZThe Dragon Demands5014364{{Quote|Well, after fifteen years in a pleasure house, I imagine just seeing the sky makes you happy.|[[Viserys Targaryen]]|Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things}}

A '''pleasure house''' is an establishment in [[Essos]] similar to a brothel. Instead of [[Prostitution|prostitutes]] that have chosen this life as a means to survive, pleasure houses usually employ bedslaves, slaves trained in the &quot;arts of love&quot; and forced to perform sexual acts for the gain of their owners.

The Free City of [[Lys]] is particularly known for its pleasure houses, which cater to every taste. The city of [[Yunkai]] in [[Slaver's Bay]] is one of the main suppliers of bedslaves for pleasure houses.
